title: AttributeError: module 'torch.cuda.profiler' has no attribute 'initialize'
body_html:
>>> with torch.autograd.profiler.profile(use_nvprof=True, trace_path='results') as prof:
...     pass
...
Traceback (most recent call last):
  File "<stdin>", line 1, in <module>
  File "/home/ahm/anaconda3/lib/python3.6/site-packages/torch/autograd/profiler.py", line 89, in __enter__
    torch.cuda.profiler.initialize()
AttributeError: module 'torch.cuda.profiler' has no attribute 'initialize'

it looks like /home/ahm/anaconda3/lib/python3.6/site-packages/torch/autograd/profiler.py just has init (which needs an output_file argument) but no initialize
